Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到漩涡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能越过那个…
