Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道不该这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我不要与行人永别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  快回来吧
