Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  生鱼片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里开始我一人去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙大人
