Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必保佑行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙大人  请息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙大人  请保佑行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从上面入口进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个炸开了一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想救行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让你一人把风头全抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真罗嗦  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不率直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不行  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不是故意的  我真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙大人  真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙大人  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙大人  请保佑公子平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请保护行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请救救行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙大人  请实现小铃和行人的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.44,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龙大人  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必保护行人  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:14:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那光芒是…那就是海龙大人的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人现在已经在漩涡外面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你所期望的吗  西部的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虎才是  不是故意让他通过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的想法都是一致的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女婿大人  如果能离开岛的话  那并不是他一人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是因为行人拥有能让大家能为之如此付出的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这微妙的刺法有点难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还…还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说这里是岛外了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是来接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平安无事啊  收到信我很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这样一来好像变成是哥哥遇难了我赶来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是好笑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  有精神就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  没事真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始就很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢  在哥哥离家出走后我就马上出海来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后所乘的船遇到暴风雨  沉入海底了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  醒来的时候已经被漂流到一个不知名的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那岛很有趣既没有电视也没有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做饭要用柴烧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼也要自己钓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜有那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  对了  那岛叫蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似是只有男人的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这些就是岛民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好人是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的担心是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别喊我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我们没有因不纯的动机对美咲有过任何侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有谁让美咲悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很笨拙  但一直被大家所帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在非常的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以还想再在蓝兰岛生活一会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听些奇闻也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  哥哥也一起过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很欢迎哥哥您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这暴风雨来之前不穿越漩涡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去是…要回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回我的 蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的…蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有人在等着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲  就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  也请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快速出发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  明明看得到岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却无论几次都被推回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然从外面进去是绝对不可能的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要跟行人永别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看着吧  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可能的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对…没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,担心女婿大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人绝对没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在一定见到妹妹美咲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记行人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还会有新的女婿大人会漂流进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆  在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说曹操曹操就到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  又相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飞蛾扑火自取灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然自愿回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二回  争夺女婿大人捉迷藏大会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  女婿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,争夺女婿大人捉迷藏大会要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,规则就不用我介绍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为何  我没听过这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女婿大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道他一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是不应该勉强回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,远野先生  吃早饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  那家伙为什么还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结束呢  还没分出胜负呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.56,0:22:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅  偷袭太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.58,0:22:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向着成熟女人前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要连骨头深处都…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…确实是竖起三根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:00.07,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（日本人用食指中指和拇指按在榻榻米上行礼）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小女不才
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  等等  请等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.34,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（新角色）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还要追吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:19.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（蓝兰岛剧终 感谢大家的收看）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:58.34,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}決めたことならば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:08.21,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}まっすぐ　そっと見つめてる　笑顔の花束抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:17.86,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}ホントはね　そんな私でいたいけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:31.44,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}やっぱりあふれる気持ち　駈け出してしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:42.02,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}ずっとそばにいて　私の大切なひと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:52.11,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}たったひとつ　かけがえない愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:18:04.64,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}せつなさの向こうに　永遠があると知った
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:20.31,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}どんなこともきっと　受け止める勇気をください
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:32.59,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}はりつめた理性　ほとばしる感情の前で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:44.32,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}こんな無力なものだとわかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:57.65,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}君を守りたい　全身全霊で　ただ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:08.44,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}愛のために　すべてを捧げて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:20.38,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}君が思うままに　自由に羽ばたくときは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:24.41,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}その瞳が…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:58.34,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}如果是决定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:08.21,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}静静地注视着你　笑脸拥抱花束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:17.86,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}其实呢　虽然是这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:31.44,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}溢满的心情果然还是　会奔涌出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:42.02,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}一直留在我的身边吧　我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:52.11,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}这唯一的　无法替代的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:18:04.64,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}我知道在痛苦的对面　就是永远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:20.31,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}无论发生什么　请给我接受下去的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:32.59,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}在布满理性　喷涌出感情的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:44.32,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}我了解到是多么的无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:57.65,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}我想守护你　只想　全身心地守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:08.44,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}为了爱　我愿意献上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:20.38,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}就如你期望的一样　展翅飞翔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:24.41,INC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}那眼神…
